                <p>In fact, the Internet is full of stories that laud the seemingly overnight success of entrepreneurs. These stories make it seem like these business owners are pure genius and that their success can be easily enjoyed by anyone else. However, in reality these overnight success stories often were preceded by years of hard work that was skillfully kept out of the public's knowledge.</p>
                
